			BREE (O.S.)
	Is Mr. Faber there?
		(beat)
	Mr. Faber Senior.

INT. GARMENT BUILDING: FABER'S OFFICE: FABER - DAY
(NIGHT)

Mr. Faber's phone buzzes; he picks it up.

			FABER
	Yes?
		(then, glancing about)
	Bree?

INT. SPANGLER (OUTER) OFFICE: BREE ON PHONE - DAY
(NIGHT)

			BREE
		(haltingly)
	-- I'm -- I just have to talk to
